<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>TAT Breached Notification</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f4f4f4;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    h1 {
      color: #ff6f61;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    table, th, td {
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      text-align: left;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #ff6f61;
      color: white;
    }
    .highlight {
      background-color: #f8d7da;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>TAT Breached Notification</h1>
  <p>Dear <%= emp_name %>,</p>
  
  <p>We are writing to inform you that the Turnaround Time (TAT) for some of your leads has been breached. Please find the details below:</p>
  
  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>ID</th>
        <th>Customer Name</th>
        <th>Phone Number</th>
        <th>Aadhar</th>
        <th>Time Elapsed</th>
        
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% leads.forEach(function(lead) { %>
        <tr class="<%= lead.isBreached ? 'highlight' : '' %>">
          <td><%= lead.id %></td>
          <td><%= lead.cust_name %></td>
          <td><%= lead.phone_no %></td>
          <td><%= lead.aadhar %> </td>
          <td><%= lead.TimeElapsed  %> days</td>
        </tr>
      <% }); %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <p>Please take immediate action to resolve the situation. If you have any questions or need further details, feel free to contact us.</p>
  
  <p>Best regards,</p>
  <p>Your Team</p>
</body>
</html>
